{
  "texts": [
    "The new school building had to offer the most suitable environment for studying and working, enrich the university campus with the best quality and sustainable architecture in mind, serve around 1,400 architecture students, and provide them with various spaces such as studios, lecture halls, and so forth.",
    "These constraints were based on the current architecture school needs.",
    "By providing a realistic design problem, we aimed to create an environment where participants would be more likely to engage with the experiment.",
    "The study participants were divided into the experimental and control groups (see the \"Participants\" section for further detail).",
    "The experimental group had conversations with the chatbot."
  ]
}